  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV6">
<l>nākamēntu mēruveṟpai nākamēntu maṇṇiṉai</l>
<l>nākamēntu mākamāka mākamēntu vārpuṉal</l>
<l>mākamēntu maṅkultīyōr vāyuvain tamaintukāt</l>
<l>tēkamēnti niṉṟanīrmai niṉkaṇēyi yaṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You whose body is borne by a serpent!</l>
<l>The nature of protecting appropriately [and] bearing single[-handedly]</l>
<l rend="indent">Mount Meru that bears heaven,</l>
<l rend="indent">the earth borne by the elephants/the snake Ananta,</l>
<l rend="indent">Heaven, the overflowing river held up by the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">the clouds held by the great space, the unique fire, the five vital airs,</l>
<l>is possible [only] to You.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
